                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">为配合即将上映的 《死侍与狼人》，Microsoft 与 Marvel Studios 合作推出一款全新 Xbox 无线手掣。上周推出的 Xbox Cheeky 手掣以死侍圆润臀部为设计灵感，今次轮到狼人，以其「Hugh Jackman 合金臀部」成为手掣卖点。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252092 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controller_wv-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controller_wv-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controller_wv.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新 Xbox 手掣最大卖点在于以影星 Hugh Jackman 的合金臀部（图片来源：<a href="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2024/07/22/deadpool-wolverine-xbox-controller-wolverine-design/">Xbox</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">新 Xbox 手掣最大卖点在于其夸张后部设计，以影星 Hugh Jackman 的合金臀部作蓝本。目前尚未清楚新设计下如何存取电池，但手掣其他功能与标准版无异。手掣设计融合狼人在电影中穿著的标志性黄色战衣，从质感、颜色到侧边蓝色细节都一一呈现。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1252107" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controllerdp_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controllerdp_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/double_controllerdp_.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">狼人手掣与死侍手掣一样，并不会公开发售。用家想要拥有它，唯一方法是参加微软在 Instagram 上举办的抽奖活动。首先要追踪微软 Xbox Instagram 帐号，按赞抽奖贴文，再留言标注三位朋友方有机会获得。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1252108" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/billboardlandscapea9-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/billboardlandscapea9-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/billboardlandscapea9.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://news.xbox.com/en-us/2024/07/22/deadpool-wolverine-xbox-controller-wolverine-design/">Xbox</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/senuas-saga-hellblade-ii-review/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】《Senua&#8217;s Saga: Hellblade II》 精神病主题黑暗风格</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/10/xbox-boss-i-think-we-should-have-a-handheld-too/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Xbox 主管暗示有意开发手提游戏机　对 Steam Deck 等游戏机很有好感</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/12/microsoft-says-it-needs-games-like-hi-fi-rush-the-day-after-killing-its-studio/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Microsoft 关闭旗下多间游戏工作室　强调需要制作「小型但有影响力的游戏」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/hugh-jackman-xbox/game-channel/">微软《死侍与狼人》 Xbox 手掣，狼人也有份 + 背面「合金臀部」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
